 *   A5 = SCL for BMP085 (I2C Wire protocol)
 *    2 = Push button for cycling through the display screens. Wired to
 *        be pulled HIGH when not pressed.
 *    3 = DS18B20 temperature sensor (direct digital read)
 *    9 = MOSI -> OLED DATA
 *   10 = CLK  -> OLED CLK
 *   11 = DC  -> OLED SAO
 *   12 = CS  -> OLED CS
 *   13 = RESET -> OLED RST
 *
